author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-CSI Compressco LP Qtrly Net Loss Per Diluted Common Unit $0.29
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Csi Compressco Lp:
* ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS * Q4 REVENUE $83.1 MILLION VERSUS $82.9 MILLION * PROJECTED 2018 TOTAL CAPITAL EXPENDITURES ARE EXPECTED TO BE BETWEEN $55 MILLION AND $75 MILLION
* QTRLY NET LOSS PER DILUTED COMMON UNIT $0.29 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $-0.24, REVENUE VIEW $75.4 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
